apology and various Malaysian government departments have been directed to
curtail contacts with Australia.
Yesterday a scheduled meeting in Kuala Lumpur between Mr Abdullah Ahmad
Badawi, Malaysia's foreign minister, and Mr Peter Cook, the visiting
Australian trade minister, was cancelled by Malaysian officials.
