Confederation Life                  0.33               1.87
Guardian Royal Exch                 0.40               1.80
Abu Dhabi Inv Auth                  0.67               1.78
Lucas Pension Trustees              0.34               1.78
Britannic Assurance                 0.51               1.76
Baillie Gifford                     0.43               1.70
Provident Mutual                    0.48               1.65
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
