FT  06 DEC 93 / Arts: Today's Television
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By CHRISTOPHER DUNKLEY
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
These days a new business guru with a miracle wheeze seems to turn up every
month, promising that our entire world is about to be revolutionised by
magnetic string or the power of diagonal thinking or some such malarkey.
Today in Crazy Ways For Crazy Days BBC2 shows guru Tom Peters addressing a
