FT  06 DEC 93 / Ramsden arrested
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Terry Ramsden, the former dealer in Japanese warrants who was given a
two-year suspended sentence last month on four charges of fraudulently
inducing investments, was arrested on Friday night in connection with his
bankruptcy arrangements.
Mr Ramsden was released on police bail for two months while City of London
police continue their inquiries.
